      Bellbowrie is the suburban heart of Brisbane's western fringe. Where neighbouring Moggill and Pinjarra Hills are acreage and rural, Bellbowrie is traditional residential: family homes on standard suburban blocks, mature street trees and an established neighbourhood feel that buyers describe as quiet and self-contained.
    </p>
<!-- APPRAISAL FORM -->
