<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I know Bellbowrie well. I understand the value-conscious family buyer who chooses Bellbowrie over Kenmore, and how to position a property to attract the buyers who actively prefer this end of the corridor. Suburban family homes need to be marketed differently to inner-city character properties, and I tailor the campaign accordingly.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Bellbowrie Shopping Plaza is the suburb's commercial anchor, providing a supermarket, medical services and everyday retail without needing to drive into Kenmore. The Moggill State School catchment is a primary value driver, and the suburb's network of parks along Moggill Creek gives families and dog owners genuine open space. Homes on the higher streets toward Birkin Road and properties with elevated rear aspects toward bushland reserves consistently sit at the upper end of suburb values.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Bellbowrie Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Western Family Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Value Family Living</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Strong upgrader and relocation demand</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/moggill" style="color:#b98229;">Moggill</a>, <a href="/suburbs/pinjarra-hills" style="color:#b98229;">Pinjarra Hills</a>, <a href="/suburbs/kenmore" style="color:#b98229;">Kenmore</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

